This alarm system represents a simple and compact solution that has been implemented for ESPhome and Homeassistant. The entire code was generated with the support of ChatGPT-4.

The recommended hardware for this project includes:

Olimex ESP32-POE-ISO
128x32 OLED 0.91" I2C (Resolution: 128x32)
4x3 Keypad Matrix (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 0, *, #)
NFC Reader, specific model: mfrc522
Door contacts, controlled via GPIO with an MCP23017 I/O expander

Please note that the code has not been verified, and its use is at your own risk.
